'''加迪迈庙'''（{{lang-en|Gadhimai Temple}}）位于[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]{{link-en|巴拉 (尼泊尔)|Bara District|巴拉县}}{{link-en|巴里亚尔普尔 (巴拉县)|Bariyarpur, Bara|巴里亚尔普尔}}，是一座[[印度教|印度教]]寺庙。<ref>世界人名翻译大辞典，中国对外翻译出版公司，1993年</ref>

==简介==
加迪迈庙位于尼泊尔南部中央，距离[[加德满都|加德满都]]160公里，靠近[[印度|印度]][[比哈尔邦|比哈尔邦]]。加迪迈庙是供奉[[印度教|印度教]]中的力量女神“加迪迈”（Gadhimai）的寺庙。<ref name="myref1">{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8375591.stm|title=Devotees flock to Nepal animal sacrifice festival|accessdate=24 November 2009|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2009-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091126040719/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8375591.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

加迪迈庙每5年举办一次[[加迪迈节|加迪迈节]]。在这个节日中，加迪迈庙及所在地区会举行大规模的[[祭祀|祭祀]]仪式，献祭大量动物以求加迪迈女神保佑人们各自实现自己的愿望。<ref name="myref3">{{Cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Indians-throng-Nepals-Gadhimai-fair-for-animal-sacrifice/articleshow/5264701.cms?referral=PM|title=Indians throng Nepal's Gadhimai fair for animal sacrifice|accessdate=24 November 2009|publisher=Times of India|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023114331/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Indians-throng-Nepals-Gadhimai-fair-for-animal-sacrifice/articleshow/5264701.cms?referral=PM|dead-url=no}}</ref>据估计，2009年加迪迈节期间，有30万到50万只动物被杀死<ref name="myref6">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/nov/24/hindu-sacrifice-gadhimai-festival-nepal|title=Hindu sacrifice of 250,000 animals begins|accessdate=24 November 2009|publisher=The Guardian|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107054804/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/nov/24/hindu-sacrifice-gadhimai-festival-nepal|dead-url=no}}</ref>，50万人来该庙参观<ref name="myref4">{{Cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/11/24/nepal.animal.sacrifice/index.html|title=Ritual animal slaughter begins in Nepal|accessdate=November 24, 2009|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2015-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107171059/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/11/24/nepal.animal.sacrifice/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。加迪迈节被认为是世界上最大规模的动物献祭。<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 网易探索 | title = 尼泊尔宰牲节残忍杀死20万头牲畜 | url = http://discover.news.163.com/09/1126/11/5P1TPLA2000125LI.html | date = 2009-11-26 | accessdate = 2011-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110718024521/http://discover.news.163.com/09/1126/11/5P1TPLA2000125LI.html | archive-date = 2011-07-18 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="myref1"/>

若干动物权利活动人士在每次举办加迪迈节之前及之中反对该节日。2009年加迪迈节引起了[[玛妮卡·甘地|玛妮卡·甘地]]、[[碧姬·芭铎|碧姬·芭铎]]等知名人士的关注，他们齐齐反对这种大规模杀戮动物的行为。<ref name="myref3">{{Cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Indians-throng-Nepals-Gadhimai-fair-for-animal-sacrifice/articleshow/5264701.cms?referral=PM|title=Indians throng Nepal's Gadhimai fair for animal sacrifice|accessdate=24 November 2009|publisher=Times of India}}</ref>尼泊尔政府官员表示，他们不能阻止许多世纪延续下来的这种传统，尽管尼泊尔和印度的动物权利活动人士对此表示反对。动物权利活动人士说，他们不指望一夜之间就结束这种行为。<ref name="myref4">{{Cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/11/24/nepal.animal.sacrifice/index.html|title=Ritual animal slaughter begins in Nepal|accessdate=November 24, 2009|publisher=CNN}}</ref>
